sequenceDiagram
    actor Doctor
    participant AsclenaAI as Asclena AI
    participant CaseRecord
    participant Episode
    participant LabResult
    participant ImagingResult

    Doctor->>AsclenaAI: 1. Ask patient-specific questions
    AsclenaAI->>CaseRecord: 2. Retrieve case context (episodes, summaries)
    AsclenaAI->>Episode: 3. Retrieve active episode context (notes, vitals)
    AsclenaAI->>LabResult: 4. Retrieve recent lab evidence
    AsclenaAI->>ImagingResult: 5. Retrieve recent imaging evidence
    AsclenaAI->>Doctor: 6. Provide analysis and recommendations